00:07:49,630 --> 00:07:51,960
At least, algorithms
we look at here.

128
00:07:51,960 --> 00:07:53,930
And that is dangerous.

129
00:07:53,930 --> 00:07:56,850
So we want relaxation
to be safe.

130
00:07:56,850 --> 00:08:02,510
