262
00:15:25,990 --> 00:15:28,710
v. Exactly right.

263
00:15:28,710 --> 00:15:29,720
Exactly right.

264
00:15:29,720 --> 00:15:30,320
Great.

265
00:15:30,320 --> 00:15:31,560
That deserves a cushion.

266
00:15:31,560 --> 00:15:33,420
